Detailed Description

PrefLangProvider is the provider to retrieve and manipulate the prefered languages of the sim (GSM 11.11 V8.2.0 10.3.1). An instance of this class is part of the Apoxi Data Control. A pointer to this provider can be retrieved from the main provider via the id:

c_preflang_provider_id

Following column ids are defined: c_lang_pref_id :NumberType

NOTE: Please do not instantiate this class.
